<li><strong>Cloud Foundry Command Line Interface (cf CLI) v7</strong>: See <a href="#cf-cli-procedures">cf CLI Procedures</a>. For additional information about cf CLI v7, see <a href="../cf-cli/v7.html">Upgrading to cf CLI v7</a>.</li>
<li> <strong>Cloud Foundry API (CAPI)</strong>: See <a href="#api-procedures">API Procedures</a>. For additional information about adding metadata with the Cloud Foundry API (CAPI), see the _Metadata_ section in the <a href="http://v3-apidocs.cloudfoundry.org">CAPI documentation</a>.
